[Rabid raccoons might lose their fear to humans and other animals and they may become slower and are brought into stupor. They present profuse salivation, indiscriminate biting and odd vocalization. It can be confused with distemper. It is very important to make sure to keep the vaccination schemes of all dogs in the area up to date, including both rabies and distemper.

A map of South Carolina, United States: https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=5792743,242. - Mod.PMB]
